$ bcdboot.exe

`bcdboot.exe` can be used to
  • copy boot files (like bootmgr?) to the EFI System Partition (ESP)
  • Update the firmware entries in the device’s NVRAM (on UEFI PCs)
  • create/update the BCD store on the ESP


